==Taariikhdiisa==
cabdulaahi bin cumar bin khadaab wuxuu ku dhashay [[makka]] 10 sano ka hor hijrada<ref name="المزي" /><ref name="الإصابة1" />, hooyadii waa [[Zeynaba binti madcuun]] oo walaal la ahayd saxaabiga [[cusmaan bin madcuun]].

Waxa uu la islaamay aabihiis asigoo qaan gaarin [[Medina|madiina]] ayuuna u la haajiray <ref name="الذهبي2">[https://islamweb.net/ar/library/index.php?page=bookcontents&ID=273&idfrom=322&idto=328&flag=0&bk_no=60&ayano=0&surano=0&bookhad=0 سير أعلام النبلاء» ومن بقايا صغار الصحابة» عبد الله بن عمر (2)] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170928223358/http://library.islamweb.net/newlibrary/display_book.php?bk_no=60&ID=273&idfrom=322&idto=328&bookid=60&startno=1|date=28 سبتمبر 2017}}</ref>.

Cabdulaahi wuxuu si fiican u dhex galay saxaabada, wuxuuna ka ag dhawaa mar walba rasuulka scw, [[Dagaalkii Beder|dagaalkii beder]] markii la gaaray waxa uu isku qoray ciidankii baxaayay laakin nabiga scw ayaa celiyay maadaama uu yaraa, isla sidoo kale [[dagaalkii uxud]]<nowiki/>na waa la celiyay, waxaa la aqbalay [[dagaalkii axzaab]] markaas uu jirsaday 15 sano, cabdulaahi oo raintaas ka hadlaayo wuxuu dhahay:

<blockquote>maalinkii beder ayaa lee bandhigay nabiga scw anoo 13 jir ah ima aqbalin, maalinkii uxud ayaa lee bandhigay anoo 14 jir ah ima aqbalin, maalinkii khandaq ayaa lee ban dhigay anoo 15 jir ah wuu I aqbalay<ref>[http://library.islamweb.net/hadith/display_hbook.php?bk_no=628&pid=323823&hid=13476 حلية الأولياء لأبي نعيم » عَبْدُ الرَّحْمَنِ بْنُ مَهْدِيٍّ - رقم الحديث: 13476] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170810090556/http://library.islamweb.net/hadith/display_hbook.php?bk_no=628&pid=323823&hid=13476|date=10 أغسطس 2017}}</ref> </blockquote>Maalinkaas ka dib cabdulaahi wuxuu kala qeyb galay nabiga scw dhamaan dagaalada sida [[beycatu ridwaan]], [[furashada makka]], iyo [[duulaankii tabuuk]] <ref name="سعد18">[https://shamela.ws/browse.php/book-1686#page-1258 الطبقات الكبرى لابن سعد - عبد الله بن عمر بن الخطاب (18)] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171109214344/http://shamela.ws/browse.php/book-1686|date=09 نوفمبر 2017}}</ref>.

=== Xiligii khulafaa raashidiin ===
waqtigii khulafa raashidiin cabdulaahi wuxuu qeyb galay furashooyinka [[shaam]], [[masar]], [[ciraaq]] [[Iiraan|faaris]] iyo [[ifriiqiya]], wuxuu xaadiray [[dagaalkii yarmuuk]] iyo [[Dagaalkii nahaawanda|nahaawanda]], ka dib wuxuu ku soo laabtay oo degay [[Medina|madiina]].

Cumar markuu dhaawacmay wuxuu dardaarmay in lix qof oo xulay iska soo doortaan khaliifka badali lahaa, waxa oona yiri "cabdulaahi bin cumar waa inuu goob joog ka noqdaa laakin talada qeyb kuma lahan".

Markii ay dhacday fitnada oo [[Cusmaan bin Cafaan|cusmaan]] gurigiisa lagu go'doomiyay cabdulaahi wuxuu qaatay seefta aabihiis wuxuuna ka ag dagaalamay cusmaan ilaa laga dilay. Kadib cabdulaahi wuu isaga fogaaday fitnada wuxuuna ka noqday dhedhexaad, [[Cali bin Abii Daalib|cali bin abii daalib]] ayaa u bandhigay inuu [[shaam]] amiir uga noqdo laakin cabdulaahi wuu iska diiday,  

